🧩 Problem 1: Employee Hierarchy
Create a class Employee with attributes name, id, and salary, and a method displayInfo().
Then, create two subclasses:
Manager with an additional attribute department
Developer with an additional attribute programmingLanguage
Override displayInfo() in both subclasses to include the extra information.
Task:
Create objects of Manager and Developer and call displayInfo() on each.
Demonstrate polymorphism using a reference of type Employee.